      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even know why i bother picking up the brush anymore. it feels like the part of me that actually saw things... the part that felt the light... it’s just gone. i look in the mirror and i don't see a person, i just see this empty shape. like the music stopped playing and the room is just... silent. i feel completely hollow.",
